<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Equation with unknown: <m>5\times9=\underline{\hspace{1 cm}}</m> or <m>9\times5=\underline{\hspace{1 cm}}</m>. Solution: 45 trees. Sample response: I counted by five 9 times. 5, 10, 15, 20, 25, 30, 35, 40, 45</li>
      <li>Equation with unknown: <m>2\times4=?</m> or <m>4\times2=?</m> Solution: 8 trees. Sample response: I know that 2 groups of 4 is 8.</li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


